		<div id="categorycontent">
			<h3>Contribute</h3>
			<blockquote>
				<h4>Report Bugs</h4>
				You can look through the list of bugs in the <a href="http://bugs.citrusdb.org/view_all_bug_page.php">Bug Tracking</a> page.  If you have found a new bug, please <a href="http://bugs.citrusdb.org/bug_report_page.php">report it</a>.  It would be helpful to sign up for a new account in the bug tracker first so you can be notified of changes to the status of your bug.
				<h4>Help other Users</h4>
				Sign up for the <a href="https://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/citrusdb-users">citrusdb-users</a> mailing list and help answer questions of other users.
				<h4>Documentation</h4>
				Contribute more and better documentation.  You can email updates to paul at citrusdb.org.
				<h4>Source Code</h4>
				Please read the <a href="coding.html">coding standards</a> and join the <a href="mailinglists.html">development mailing list</a> to post your ideas to get started.
				<h4>Translations</h4>
				You can help by updating the translations included with the release or contribute new translation files.  The us-english file is always the most up-to-date.  Please use that to begin any new translations.  Email them to: paul at citrusdb.org.
			<h4>Let the world know about CitrusDB</h4>
			Write about this project or link to us on your website or blog.  Comment on or rate this project at <a href="http://freshmeat.net/projects/citrusdb/">freshmeat.net</a>.   Vote for or review this project at <a href="http://www.hotscripts.com/Detailed/37688.html">Hotscripts.com</a>. 
			<h4>Donations</h4>	
			Donate money to this project via <a href="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_xclick&business=paul%40citrusdb%2eorg&item_name=CitrusDB%2eorg&no_shipping=0&no_note=1&tax=0&currency_code=USD">paypal</a>.  Donations will be used for the promotion of CitrusDB and put towards new machines and internet infrastructure. 
			<p>
			</blockquote>
